data.title: About: Jamal Jones (basketball)
data.meta_description: Jamal Avery Jones (born February 17, 1993) is an American professional basketball player for Dinamo Sassari of the Italian Lega Basket Serie A (LBA). He played college basketball at Ole Miss and Texas A&M.
data.text:
dbo:abstract

Ο Τζαμάλ Τζόουνς (αγγλικά:Jamal Jones, 17 Φεβρουαρίου 1993) είναι Αμερικανός επαγγελματίας καλαθοσφαιριστής, ο οποίος αγωνίζεται ως σούτινγκ γκαρντ/σμολ φόργουορντ για τον Ιωνικό Νίκαιας. (el)

Jamal Avery Jones (Searcy, Arkansas, Estados Unidos; 17 de febrero de 1993) es un jugador estadounidense de baloncesto que actualmente juega en el Dinamo Basket Sassari de la Lega Basket Serie A. (es)

Jamal Avery Jones (born February 17, 1993) is an American professional basketball player for Dinamo Sassari of the Italian Lega Basket Serie A (LBA). He played college basketball at Ole Miss and Texas A&M. (en)

Jamal Jones, né le 17 février 1993, à Searcy, en Arkansas, est un joueur américain de basket-ball. Il évolue au poste d'ailier. (fr)

Jamal Jones (Searcy, 17 febbraio 1993) è un cestista statunitense, professionista in Europa e NBA D-League, ala grande della Dinamo Sassari. (it)
